quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,9,"(Jantee) tuma nde faabinorano…óon Joomi mon O jaabinani on : \"Min ko Mi …ďeydiroowo on ujunere e Malaa'ika jokkondiroo…ďe"
  8,10,"Alla wa…óiraali …óum si wanaa welo-welo e fii no …ďer…óe mon dee∆īira …óum. Balla wonaali si wanaa immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  8,11,"E Tuma nde ŇčoŇčre nden hippaynoo on hoolaare immorde ka Makko, Himo Jippinana on ndiyam immorde ka kammu fii yo O la…ď…ďinir on …óam, O ittana on so…ďe seytaane, e fii yo O tii…óinir (…óum) e …ďer…óe mon O tabintinira …óam teppe [mon] …óen"
  8,12,"Tuma nde Joomi maa wahyinaynoo e Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďe : \"Min Mi…óo wonndi e mo'on : tabintinee gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Arma Mi bugoo …óen∆īere e …ďer…óe heefer…ďe …ďen. Tappee dow daa…óe …óen tappon e ma…ď…ďe kala wunnjere"
  8,13,"∆äum, ko fii kam…ďe …ďe lunndike Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on. \"Kala non lunndii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, pellet, Alla ko sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  8,14,"∆äum moo…óon ; mee…óee …óum ! E wonnde pellet, no waadani heefer…ďe …ďen lepte Yiite"
  8,15,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, si on hawrii e …ďen heefer…ďe ko …ďe moo…ďii…ďe, wata on huccintinan …ďe …ďabbe …óen"
  8,16,"Kala hunccintin…óo …ďe nden √Īalnde (…ďabbal mu'un), -si wanaa hara ko on he…ď…ďitantoo…óo hare nden, maa hara ko ukkitotoo…óo e fedde, -gom…óii haray o ruttodii e tikkere immorde ka Alla, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Jahannama nge bonii ruttorde"
